homeowners on loans from Pounds 3,000 to Pounds 15,000 with a repayment
period fo 3 to 25 years. The rate is variable. The administration fee is
Pounds 50.
The unsecured Xtraloan is for Halifax customers on loans of Pounds 1,000 to
Pounds 7,500. The discounted rate is 19.1 per cent APR; it is guaranteed not
to change during the repayment period of one to five years. The
adminstration fee is Pounds 10.
